snippet.textDisplay: You know I was fine with the show runners killing off Carl if the story was going a completely different direction but the fact that they did the whispers storyline makes me feel better about dropping the show after he was killed off. He was integral part to that arc and was stillin there till the comics end (good timing on ending it). I still think someone did it as f-u to the actor for some reason. The kid was basing his life about being on the show. Personal gripes aside I wish the best to the cast and crew.
